dataIdInfo.idAbs: The dataset represents the districts and self-governing cities of Georgia. Administrative level 2 features are unavailable for Tbilisi, the Autonomous Republic of Abkhazia, and for the area known as the Provisional Administration.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Fixed multipart sliver errors in units "Dusheti", "Kareli" and "Mtskheta". 2. 7 English names in Admin2 had inconsistent Georgian names: "Akhaltsikhe", "Ambrolauri", "Gori", "Mtskheta", "Ozurgeti", "Telavi", "Zugdidi". These differences were caused by some Georgian names having extra character "ქ." that wasn't reflected in the English name. This was fixed. English names for cities with Georgian character "ქ." now have "City" in their name. 3. A gap was fixed between the borders of units "Khelvachauri" and "Keda".
